{"tid":276132,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［劣食台］老麥判官","createTime":"2017-06-08T14:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T23:17:43.000Z","uid":14578,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"afd238f115d3d4e02e0e6266c446645bacd9dc89","tid":276132,"uid":14578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T14:36:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/08/222937_5a49c473262e701e39cef08242cafe44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F08%2F222937_5a49c473262e701e39cef08242cafe44.jpg&h=7cd3a90c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n收工經過老麥，見到新包，當然要判一判佢罪啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/08/223027_d6ef777d3f4f9d8544d11e301eb9316a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F08%2F223027_d6ef777d3f4f9d8544d11e301eb9316a.jpg&h=bc690496&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多菜，仲有強加安格斯牛。講真，份量比起上次個是拉差炸雞扒強少好多。入面加左脆蒜同埋洋蔥汁，所以就叫泰脆洋蔥安格斯。<br />\n<br />\n第一口咬落去，個塊芝士味同塊強個味道好重。但屌你，個牛味同洋蔥汁呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個脆脆呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/08/223254_b2d3d828000ad647050075263df174cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F08%2F223254_b2d3d828000ad647050075263df174cc.jpg&h=d7fe3484&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦，見旁邊多汁就咬落去試真啲。個汁個味...係Lays薯片洋蔥味個隻味道，唔算太差嘅。話時話，一開始見個包咁多菜，但食到中間，竟然少少菜嘅咬口都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外，個安格斯牛有啲乾，同埋啲蒜片有少少多餘，第一個味太重，第二個脆脆口感幫唔到個包加分。<br />\n<br />\n比分時間，整體我會比六分（十分滿分）。個洋蔥汁可以落多少少，Garlic片可以整走，再加多啲菜，塊牛好難有大進步（始終係老麥）。不過，想係老麥食牛就建議菇牛包，要清新就食田園包。<br />\n<br />\n（想食好西，屌，唔好食老麥啦，老撚土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"1eed54900051471a86332db789535746629880b9","tid":276132,"uid":1134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T20:20:24.000Z","msg":"真係好撚慘打到論文咁款無人覆之餘仲要收負皮<br />\n你收皮吧啦判官"},{"pid":"a61939f31900aaf608208579d2c82a1d7e73706b","tid":276132,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T23:13:15.000Z","msg":"個汁底好味wor<br />\n牛肉貴一定細塊過雞扒"},{"pid":"100716d4d947b327972bc162801d7d6f5c77cdee","tid":276132,"uid":106468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T23:17:43.000Z","msg":"都唔識評 先入為主曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}